lyTime":"2020-01-25T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"物競天擇"},{"pid":"87e51154d94bad6bc5488e0814f4f6dd498c6a24","tid":1840562,"uid":13176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"話就話經歷過03年沙士，但出到街8成戴口罩既都係後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問老嗰輩03年係經歷咗d咩？咁低劣防護意識既人竟然都未被淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdce6e49b1c1e356220527307c4d3663e85de59d","tid":1840562,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:45:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"226240e12b57fca03e50efa27721ed40e22c2187","tid":1840562,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"唔撚戴 想攬炒 中招一定去警署 <br />\n原來你地口中嘅攬炒得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c96053972c281a6a255572cbc94d2ecf93be18e","tid":1840562,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:47:05.000Z","msg":"相信好多人屋企人都堅持唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫佢戴淨係嗯 又係咁咳 搞到我驚到失眠"},{"pid":"51b5e3eb97560f8168ff0da3183889dbb41b6759","tid":1840562,"uid":257272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"真攬炒."},{"pid":"0cff1b408d457c33183149d2a4c2527c76303f7c","tid":1840562,"uid":74405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:52:33.000Z","msg":"30歲以上應該記憶猶新<br />\n竟然仲係咁on9"},{"pid":"a4e3a9200c38872b6c2b3e8e94a6307e3da61348","tid":1840562,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:26:09.000Z","msg":"諗深一層其實係好事嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404c2586e3eddb340afc364becdfda1e06b68142","tid":1840562,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"廢中廢老 藍絲 大陸蝗<br />\n佢地信黨"},{"pid":"e594ca49f05e663e3156a10a7fa8ae4db27a5aa5","tid":1840562,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"609ab67864d5ceab88f57d39740d0011b97743c1","tid":1840562,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avXOUP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavXOUP4.jpg&h=0d52e9f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"冇晒-o-o同deadbody，變晒呢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e55b8620eee57f46639372073a7dbd007271ace","tid":1840562,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e51154d94bad6bc5488e0814f4f6dd498c6a24","tid":1840562,"uid":13176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"話就話經歷過03年沙士，但出到街8成戴口罩既都係後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問老嗰輩03年係經歷咗d咩？咁低劣防護意識既人竟然都未被淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"呢班人就係覺得<br />\n自己捱得過沙士 有抗體/無事嘅"}]}